play around in the kitchen.

775
00:39:05,691 --> 00:39:07,909
- [both chuckle]
- Oh, no, not again.

776
00:39:07,910 --> 00:39:09,868
- [Carol] I wonder what he'll whip up tonight.
- [chuckles]

