suitable place for us to settle.

1338
01:09:48,967 --> 01:09:53,362
Yes, we were looking for a
building to house our team.

1339
01:09:53,363 --> 01:09:54,928
But I had absolutely no idea

1340
01:09:54,929 --> 01:09:57,017
