1350
01:10:22,696 --> 01:10:24,959
[exhales and stutters] I just
didn't think it mattered.

1351
01:10:25,960 --> 01:10:27,961
I mean, the further
along things went,

1352
01:10:27,962 --> 01:10:30,529
