could just trip things up.

1355
01:10:41,149 --> 01:10:45,371
I kind of like just being
run-of-the-mill John.

1356
01:10:48,548 --> 01:10:50,028
Yeah, well, I did too.

1357
01:10:59,559 --> 01:11:00,691
[John] Please.

1358
01:11:01,996 --> 01:11:03,433
