[light emotional music]

1381
01:12:24,427 --> 01:12:25,732
It's time.

1382
01:12:28,431 --> 01:12:29,432
Come on.

1383
01:12:42,488 --> 01:12:43,794
[both giggles]

1384
01:12:50,409 --> 01:12:51,628
