treat for all of you.</i>

1460
01:18:58,124 --> 01:19:02,040
<i>A closing duet featuring Abigail
Simpson and her very special guest,</i>

1461
01:19:02,041 --> 01:19:06,349
<i>His Royal Highness Prince
John Lackland of Donegal.</i>

1462
01:19:06,350 --> 01:19:08,046
What're you doing out here?

1463
01:19:08,047 --> 01:19:09,134
